data.description: Built in the heart of Almaden Valley, 1046 Kiser Drive isn't merely a house, it's a home. This 3bd/2bth, two-story cozy masterpiece is located in a quiet, safe, and scenic neighborhood, that's PERFECT for the ENTIRE family! With shuttle buses for Apple / Google / Amazon employees to accommodate morning commutes AND Award Winning Schools for the kids (Graystone Elementary, Bret Harte Middle School, Leland High School). Wanna get away? Take advantage of nearby parks & trails such as Los Alamitos Creek Trail, Calero Lake, and one of the Bay Area's best...Quicksilver. Spacious, high ceilings, well-kept, with a gorgeous backyard patio that includes a storage shed & space for a recreational vehicle. Needless to say, this is a must see!
